Here are the steps to run this project:

#1 - cd into the Project root folder
#2- run sudo npm install
#3- run bower install
#4- if you dont have mongodb installed run: brew install mongodb
#5- run mongod --config /usr/local/etc/mongod.conf (to run mongodb database)
#6- run grunt serve (this runs grunt serve for frontend and node server for backend)
#7- cd into <project-root>/RememeberLinks/node_modules/mongo-express
#8- copy content of config.default.js into a new file called config.js (if this doesnt exist)
#9- run node app (in order to run mongo-express, this is a Admin UI for mongodb url is http://localhost:8081)